{"tid":879482,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發左個怪夢 求解讀","createTime":"2018-10-28T03:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T04:52:27.000Z","uid":185502,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"21618c53da8910f5cb53b8d46289f03e1bf6fac7","tid":879482,"uid":185502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T03:49:41.000Z","msg":"被ex分手兩個月<br />\n琴晚發左個夢，係街度突然撞到ex，佢都自己一個行緊，跟著一齊傾計有講有笑，有d令人回想起以前既快樂時光。<br />\n<br />\n突然風雲變色落好大雨，我地都冇帶遮，佢就好急咁話要去的士站飛的走，<br />\n而我就話 &ldquo;我陪你搵啦&rdquo;，<br />\n但佢就話 &ldquo;你自己搵的士搭啦&rdquo;，<br />\n跟著就自己冒雨跑走左，剩低我一個係度淋雨。<br />\n<br />\n我係雨中望住佢跑走既背影呆左陣，就諗住淋著雨慢慢行去地鐵站，反正都冇咩心情。<br />\n<br />\n行左陣，突然停雨烏雲走哂，心諗咩事啊，但另轉頭就見到一班好耐冇見既兄弟都濕哂身係後面行緊，原來佢地頭先都係行緊去地鐵站，我仲笑佢地乜頭先成班男人雨中漫步咁浪漫啊。<br />\n跟著就天朗氣清咁同佢地一邊敍舊，一邊有講有笑咁一齊行<br />\n<br />\n之後就夢醒左<br />\n其實我都估到個夢想同我講咩，但點解會發埋呢d夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd24b57f77c49b265f71f501192605038171fe43","tid":879482,"uid":138138,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T03:50:47.000Z","msg":"gay撚到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/28/115045_ea4cbd43d2ad1932058e1ab87a595774.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F28%2F115045_ea4cbd43d2ad1932058e1ab87a595774.jpg&h=eb6f151c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df5c9faf97654355d0dcbca572ef375975bdafaf","tid":879482,"uid":175710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd24b57f77c49b265f71f501192605038171fe43","tid":879482,"uid":138138,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T03:50:47.000Z","msg":"gay撚到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/28/115045_ea4cbd43d2ad1932058e1ab87a595774.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F28%2F115045_ea4cbd43d2ad1932058e1ab87a595774.jpg&h=eb6f151c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T04:46:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74a8724a9955ffb1cd0392f3c80e2da5a8bd985","tid":879482,"uid":218915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T04:52:27.000Z","msg":"你太掛住佢 個潛意識未放底佢 但係因為之前分手 令你潛意識都覺得再見番都係會比人拋底 <br />\n所以先會發呢種夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}